1
00:00:00,340 --> 00:00:01,740
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,740 --> 00:00:03,380
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,440 --> 00:00:05,140
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:08,050 --> 00:00:10,650
You and me. The two of us.

5
00:00:11,950 --> 00:00:14,620
For 30 years, we've fought
to take control of Adele...

6
00:00:15,090 --> 00:00:16,420
from Park Tae Ho.

7
00:00:18,660 --> 00:00:22,930
And for me, those 30 years
feel like a complete waste.

8
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:29,170
How about we finally put an end
to this tiresome fight?

9
00:00:30,870 --> 00:00:32,800
Park Tae Ho is out of commission,

10
00:00:33,770 --> 00:00:36,470
and Adele is more than big enough
for both of us.

11
00:00:37,580 --> 00:00:38,580
What?

12
00:00:39,840 --> 00:00:41,310
We'll sideline Park Tae Ho...

13
00:00:41,950 --> 00:00:43,350
and split Adele between us.

14
00:00:43,780 --> 00:00:47,050
We'll each take the firms we want
and split them fairly, fifty-fifty.

15
00:00:48,620 --> 00:00:52,160
If our sons each take over
a part of Adele,

16
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:56,760
don't you think they could get along
without fighting one another?

17
00:00:58,400 --> 00:01:01,370
If I keep your son's secret buried,

18
00:01:02,130 --> 00:01:03,740
you'll give me half of Adele?

19
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:05,240
Well?

20
00:01:06,070 --> 00:01:08,740
It's an offer too good to refuse,
wouldn't you say?

21
00:01:21,990 --> 00:01:25,290
First, I want to know
what you did...

22
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:27,290
to the chairman.

23
00:01:27,390 --> 00:01:28,930
That's none of your business.

24
00:01:29,730 --> 00:01:32,330
Let's just say Park Tae Ho
will never wake up.

25
00:01:33,900 --> 00:01:34,930
In that case...

26
00:01:39,270 --> 00:01:40,540
I have to admit, it's a good deal.

27
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:43,040
Right?

28
00:01:43,910 --> 00:01:45,540
Then, we'll do as I said...

29
00:01:46,510 --> 00:01:47,550
No way.

30
00:01:48,350 --> 00:01:49,850
I was outside. I heard everything.

31
00:01:50,180 --> 00:01:52,620
How could you even consider
such a ridiculous offer?

32
00:01:54,650 --> 00:01:55,720
Father.

33
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:59,790
Father. Father, wake up. Please?

34
00:02:00,230 --> 00:02:02,160
Father!

35
00:02:02,730 --> 00:02:03,730
Min Jun.

36
00:02:05,060 --> 00:02:06,930
You put my father in this state,

37
00:02:07,730 --> 00:02:09,600
and now you think
you can take over the company?

38
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,800
No.

39
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:15,670
You're not getting your way.
I won't let you.

40
00:02:19,440 --> 00:02:23,080
I'm handing you over to the police
so you can pay for what you've done.

41
00:02:23,450 --> 00:02:26,350
Let go of me!
How dare you lay a hand on me?

42
00:02:29,090 --> 00:02:30,960
- You...
- Min Jun.

43
00:02:31,020 --> 00:02:32,320
I said, let go of me!

44
00:02:32,820 --> 00:02:33,830
Yes, James.

45
00:02:34,730 --> 00:02:36,630
Thanks to the intel team,
I made it out safely.

46
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:40,200
I'll go in, see what's going on,
and call you back.

47
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,000
Okay.

48
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,840
Let's go in.

49
00:02:47,070 --> 00:02:48,710
Overlooking what my mom did...

50
00:02:50,210 --> 00:02:51,710
will help with your plan, right?

51
00:02:53,210 --> 00:02:54,380
Because she has
his power of attorney,

52
00:02:54,980 --> 00:02:57,020
she can take control of Adele Group.

53
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:11,130
- Let go of me. Hey!
- Min Jun.

54
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:14,000
If I had known this would happen,
I'd never have let you off the hook.

55
00:03:14,600 --> 00:03:18,400
When I knew you tried to kill me,
I should've turned you in to police.

56
00:03:18,870 --> 00:03:21,410
But since I'd lost my memory,
I kept wondering why.

57
00:03:21,670 --> 00:03:25,180
For Hyun Jun's sake, I waited.
That was a mistake.

58
00:03:25,180 --> 00:03:28,480
Jung Ran! Let go of her, will you?

59
00:03:28,950 --> 00:03:31,820
- You little...
- Jung Ran, please!

60
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:33,050
Calm down already.

61
00:03:33,180 --> 00:03:35,150
Min Jun, that's enough.

62
00:03:35,650 --> 00:03:37,090
This isn't going to solve anything.

63
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:39,190
Mother?

64
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:41,660
Kim Myung Hui,
give me a straight answer.

65
00:03:42,130 --> 00:03:43,600
Will we fight this
to the bitter end,

66
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,430
or will you settle
for half of the group?

67
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:49,530
- Everyone, just calm down.
- No.

68
00:03:49,930 --> 00:03:52,470
Half or not,
I don't want to hear another word.

69
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:54,910
I'm turning her in
to the police right now.

70
00:03:55,210 --> 00:03:56,640
Hey, wait!

71
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:59,680
Park Min Jun!
What do you think you're doing?

72
00:03:59,740 --> 00:04:01,250
It's your mom!

73
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:05,080
She put our father in a coma.

74
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:08,820
What?

75
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,060
She put our father in a coma?

76
00:04:11,290 --> 00:04:14,230
And she has the nerve to suggest
we act like nothing happened,

77
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:15,830
but I can't do that.

78
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:20,000
I'm turning her over to the police,
so get out of my way.

79
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:22,500
Stay out of this!

80
00:04:23,170 --> 00:04:25,170
My business is with your mother.

81
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:30,940
- Min Jun.
- No. I don't care what you say.

82
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:34,980
You're a murderer
who tried to kill me and Father.

83
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:37,480
What? A murderer?

84
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:39,680
Hey, watch your mouth.

85
00:04:40,690 --> 00:04:43,520
How can you take her side
after all this?

86
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,660
Stop it, you two.

87
00:04:48,590 --> 00:04:52,530
To be blunt, you and Park Tae Ho
are alive and well.

88
00:04:52,660 --> 00:04:55,100
- Why are you calling me a murderer?
- Mom, stop it.

89
00:04:55,970 --> 00:04:56,970
See?

90
00:04:57,670 --> 00:04:59,670
I have amnesia
and Father's in a coma,

91
00:04:59,670 --> 00:05:01,240
but she says we're fine.

92
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:04,480
She still has no clue
what she did wrong.

93
00:05:06,610 --> 00:05:07,810
I'm turning her over to the police.

94
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:10,980
That's enough.
Don't blow this out of proportion.

95
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,920
You want to be like your mother?

96
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,950
Park Min Jun!

97
00:05:15,020 --> 00:05:16,420
I said, stop it.

98
00:05:17,190 --> 00:05:18,590
You think I'm scared of the police?

99
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:20,960
Call them right now.

100
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,860
Jung Ran!

101
00:05:26,260 --> 00:05:27,430
Enough!

102
00:05:43,250 --> 00:05:45,120
Don't tell me you're doing this
because of her offer.

103
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:49,350
Were you so tempted by her offer
to split Adele Group in half...

104
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:52,590
that you'd abandon Father
and look the other way?

105
00:05:53,390 --> 00:05:55,360
This is the best option
we have right now.

106
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:58,460
We can't prove her crimes
to the police.

107
00:05:58,460 --> 00:05:59,700
If she uses her power of attorney,

108
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:01,700
we'll be
at an even greater disadvantage.

109
00:06:02,430 --> 00:06:05,870
If this fight escalates, you
and Hyun Jun will get hurt again.

110
00:06:06,070 --> 00:06:08,170
- Is that what you want?
- Even so,

111
00:06:08,370 --> 00:06:10,340
we can't just leave Father this way.

112
00:06:17,820 --> 00:06:20,520
Please, be realistic.

113
00:06:28,930 --> 00:06:30,030
I'm lying.

114
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:32,960
This is all to trick Oh Jung Ran.

115
00:06:33,030 --> 00:06:35,000
(I'm lying.
This is all to trick Oh Jung Ran.)

116
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:52,250
For my father's sake,
I can't accept this.

117
00:06:52,450 --> 00:06:56,120
I want to turn her in to the police
and take Father to the hospital now.

118
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:57,460
But...

119
00:06:58,860 --> 00:07:00,460
If this is what you want, Mother,

120
00:07:01,660 --> 00:07:02,990
I'll try to hold back.

121
00:07:14,940 --> 00:07:16,840
This is so wrong!

122
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:22,180
Jung Ran!

123
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:24,850
Hyun Jun, oh no.

124
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:39,460
Stop it!

125
00:07:40,670 --> 00:07:42,930
You sided with me against Min Jun,
so what changed?

126
00:07:43,330 --> 00:07:45,140
That's what's driving me crazy.

127
00:07:46,740 --> 00:07:49,210
I'm trying my best
to understand you, Mom.

128
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:54,680
I'm...

129
00:07:55,850 --> 00:07:57,480
I'm trying to put up with it,

130
00:07:58,550 --> 00:07:59,780
but you make my blood boil.

131
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:01,220
How...

132
00:08:03,150 --> 00:08:04,760
How could a person be like this?

133
00:08:05,820 --> 00:08:07,930
You got caught
trying to kill Min Jun,

134
00:08:08,690 --> 00:08:10,530
and because you were afraid...

135
00:08:10,860 --> 00:08:13,660
of being divorced and thrown out,
you did this to Father?

136
00:08:15,130 --> 00:08:18,870
The shame and disgust
you make me feel drive me insane!

137
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:22,210
Hyun Jun, please.

138
00:08:22,210 --> 00:08:25,080
Ashamed of who? And of what?

139
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,050
Park Min Jun and Kim Myung Hui?

140
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,880
They act all high and mighty,

141
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:31,250
but they're just
materialistic snobs too.

142
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:35,290
I offered her half of Adele,
and she agreed to let this slide.

143
00:08:35,620 --> 00:08:37,390
And in the end, Park Min Jun...

144
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:39,920
is bound to do
whatever his mother wants.

145
00:08:40,290 --> 00:08:41,290
What?

146
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:43,530
Half of Adele Group?

147
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:47,270
So you need to make a clear decision
right here, right now.

148
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:50,800
You may not get control of Adele
if your father wakes up.

149
00:08:50,870 --> 00:08:53,440
Will you throw your mother in prison
and give up all of it?

150
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:55,540
Just so you know,

151
00:08:56,340 --> 00:08:59,210
I could've come back after killing
both Kim Myung Hui and Park Min Jun.

152
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:00,850
Jung Ran!

153
00:09:02,180 --> 00:09:03,450
Mom!

154
00:09:03,450 --> 00:09:05,120
You're the reason I didn't!

155
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:08,690
I didn't think you could handle it
if I killed all of them.

156
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:10,860
That's why I stopped after dealing
with Park Tae Ho.

157
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:12,690
If I take this any further,

158
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:15,490
it'll get bloody.
Either they die or I do.

159
00:09:15,490 --> 00:09:17,030
Is that what you want?

160
00:09:18,230 --> 00:09:19,460
Should I keep going?

161
00:09:21,830 --> 00:09:22,970
That's enough.

162
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:28,040
He can barely handle this situation.
How can you hound him like this?

163
00:09:28,670 --> 00:09:32,280
After all, you're his parents.

164
00:09:33,310 --> 00:09:36,150
Hyun Jun is the one
who's suffering the most right now.

165
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:39,080
She's right.

166
00:09:39,750 --> 00:09:42,990
You need to think about
Hyun Jun's feelings too.

167
00:09:46,490 --> 00:09:49,690
Hyun Jun... Oh, man. Hyun Jun!

168
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,600
Hyun Jun!

169
00:09:59,900 --> 00:10:01,770
What? What is it?

170
00:10:03,710 --> 00:10:05,180
On Hyun Jun's behalf,

171
00:10:05,610 --> 00:10:09,050
I think I need to know
what your plan is.

172
00:10:10,380 --> 00:10:12,780
President Kim Myung Hui
and Park Min Jun.

173
00:10:13,420 --> 00:10:14,820
What are you going to do about them?

174
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:21,490
Are you really going
to give them half of Adele...

175
00:10:21,590 --> 00:10:23,490
and end this fight?

176
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:28,330
Or are you using
half of Adele as bait...

177
00:10:28,770 --> 00:10:31,040
to destroy them both?

178
00:10:43,050 --> 00:10:46,650
We'll pretend to accept her offer
of splitting Adele...

179
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:48,790
and keep an eye on the chairman.

180
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:53,460
If he wakes up,
we can take down Oh Jung Ran.

181
00:10:53,520 --> 00:10:56,130
Were you planning on tricking them
from the start?

182
00:10:56,430 --> 00:10:57,760
You never intended...

183
00:10:57,960 --> 00:11:00,000
to accept the offer at all?

184
00:11:00,260 --> 00:11:01,270
Not for a second.

185
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:05,540
I won't share Adele or anything else
with Oh Jung Ran.

186
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:08,340
I'll make you Adele's sole owner,

187
00:11:09,070 --> 00:11:13,140
and I will make them pay
for trying to kill you.

188
00:11:13,910 --> 00:11:16,850
And for killing my sister
all those years ago.

189
00:11:24,160 --> 00:11:25,720
To be honest,

190
00:11:26,690 --> 00:11:28,930
I want to kill Kim Myung Hui
and Park Min Jun.

191
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:33,730
But you can't always get your way,
can you?

192
00:11:35,030 --> 00:11:38,770
Even for me,
killing them both is a bit much.

193
00:11:39,370 --> 00:11:42,440
Also, Hyun Jun will be a wreck.
It'll be impossible to clean up.

194
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:47,310
That's why I'm settling
for splitting Adele in half.

195
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:51,280
What?

196
00:11:51,850 --> 00:11:53,050
Don't you believe me?

197
00:11:55,190 --> 00:11:59,860
It's hard to believe you'd give away
half of the company so easily.

198
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:01,690
You put the chairman
out of commission...

199
00:12:01,690 --> 00:12:03,330
and now hold his power of attorney,

200
00:12:03,530 --> 00:12:05,600
yet you're still playing it safe.

201
00:12:06,630 --> 00:12:09,730
Do they have
some kind of dirt on you?

202
00:12:10,770 --> 00:12:13,540
There's no need to tell her
about Hyun Jun's secret.

203
00:12:14,770 --> 00:12:16,410
Dirt on me? As if.

204
00:12:17,610 --> 00:12:20,680
I'm just being careful
and making sure this ends perfectly.

205
00:12:21,150 --> 00:12:23,550
I know exactly how vicious
Kim Myung Hui can be.

206
00:12:24,380 --> 00:12:26,450
The reason
I had Hyun Jun locked up...

207
00:12:26,450 --> 00:12:29,620
was to protect him
from Myung Hui and her people.

208
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,760
By the way, how did you two
get out of there?

209
00:12:34,490 --> 00:12:36,830
My dad found us and got us out.

210
00:12:42,630 --> 00:12:44,600
What is it? Why are you here?

211
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:48,340
I'm here to tell you
I got Min Jun to reconsider.

212
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:49,470
Listen to you.

213
00:12:50,470 --> 00:12:51,680
Dropping the formalities, are we?

214
00:12:53,010 --> 00:12:55,450
There's no reason to treat you
as the lady of the family...

215
00:12:55,450 --> 00:12:56,880
when your husband isn't
in the picture.

216
00:12:58,050 --> 00:13:02,790
Since we agreed to split everything,
I'd say that makes us equals.

217
00:13:02,850 --> 00:13:04,390
Equals?

218
00:13:06,320 --> 00:13:08,890
Fine. Have at it.

219
00:13:10,790 --> 00:13:11,860
But...

220
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:14,930
I have to ask.

221
00:13:17,570 --> 00:13:21,510
Could he still hear us
even though he's in this state?

222
00:13:21,610 --> 00:13:25,310
How could he?
I told you, Park Tae Ho is out cold.

223
00:13:25,940 --> 00:13:28,280
I keep telling you
that he can't wake up.

224
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:29,650
He can...

225
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:32,150
never wake up?

226
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:39,860
Chloe, you're awfully calm
for a situation like this.

227
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:43,460
Shouldn't you be scared
and running for the hills?

228
00:13:44,430 --> 00:13:46,430
Maybe you should reconsider
this marriage.

229
00:13:47,830 --> 00:13:50,670
The moment I decided
to marry Hyun Jun,

230
00:13:51,300 --> 00:13:54,170
I made up my mind...

231
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:56,440
that I'd never back down.

232
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:59,040
Especially in a situation like this,

233
00:14:01,580 --> 00:14:02,580
there's no way...

234
00:14:03,610 --> 00:14:05,180
I'm backing down.

235
00:14:05,780 --> 00:14:06,850
We'll see.

236
00:14:07,850 --> 00:14:11,860
Will you still feel the same way
after you get your memory back?

237
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:14,730
On the day
of the hit-and-run accident...

238
00:14:14,790 --> 00:14:17,290
Why are you meddling
in my son's marriage?

239
00:14:17,930 --> 00:14:21,200
I appreciate your concern,
but I don't need you to interfere.

240
00:14:22,100 --> 00:14:24,740
My past memories aren't
as important...

241
00:14:24,870 --> 00:14:27,300
as the decision
I'm making right now.

242
00:14:27,370 --> 00:14:31,240
Good. That's the kind of grit
my daughter-in-law should have.

243
00:14:45,660 --> 00:14:47,260
No one's picking up.

244
00:14:48,760 --> 00:14:52,200
I guess I'll have to go see
what's happening for myself.

245
00:15:13,520 --> 00:15:14,790
Manager Kang,

246
00:15:16,220 --> 00:15:19,090
I thought you were completely loyal
to the chairman.

247
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:22,590
Did you betray him
because Oh Jung Ran got to you?

248
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:27,230
I didn't betray the chairman.

249
00:15:29,070 --> 00:15:32,740
I had no choice.
I have a family to protect, too.

250
00:15:37,010 --> 00:15:38,010
And...

251
00:15:38,640 --> 00:15:40,280
what if the chairman wakes up?

252
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:42,450
What are you going to do then?

253
00:15:43,180 --> 00:15:44,750
If he wakes up,

254
00:15:46,450 --> 00:15:49,520
of course I'll go right back
to my post.

255
00:15:57,730 --> 00:16:00,160
To bring down Oh Jung Ran right now,

256
00:16:00,530 --> 00:16:02,530
we need Chairman Park to wake up.

257
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:05,240
But how am I supposed to wake him?

258
00:16:06,740 --> 00:16:07,740
Ma'am.

259
00:16:11,480 --> 00:16:13,410
What brings you here, Ms. Choi?

260
00:16:13,410 --> 00:16:15,350
I couldn't get ahold of anyone.

261
00:16:18,050 --> 00:16:19,780
I need a word with you.

262
00:16:25,060 --> 00:16:26,160
Ma'am.

263
00:16:28,660 --> 00:16:29,790
Mrs. Ok.

264
00:16:30,830 --> 00:16:34,300
Ms. Choi told me.
She said you were kicked out.

265
00:16:34,770 --> 00:16:37,300
Things have been so chaotic
that I couldn't check on you.

266
00:16:38,070 --> 00:16:41,740
Not at all. I didn't know what was
going on in the house either,

267
00:16:41,810 --> 00:16:45,180
so I couldn't call.
That's why I asked to meet you here.

268
00:16:46,210 --> 00:16:48,850
Are you all right, ma'am?

269
00:16:49,150 --> 00:16:52,020
Yes. I think we've bought some time,
for now.

270
00:16:52,950 --> 00:16:56,920
By any chance, did you find out
what Ms. Oh did...

271
00:16:56,920 --> 00:16:58,260
to the chairman?

272
00:16:58,660 --> 00:17:01,990
That's why I came here.
I have something to tell you.

273
00:17:02,690 --> 00:17:04,160
What do you mean?

274
00:17:04,500 --> 00:17:07,060
Right after Ms. Oh came back,
I noticed...

275
00:17:07,530 --> 00:17:09,100
she was following a schedule
for something.

276
00:17:09,430 --> 00:17:11,700
She even set alarms
to keep track of it.

277
00:17:12,070 --> 00:17:13,070
No...

278
00:17:20,340 --> 00:17:22,280
She even stopped throwing a fit...

279
00:17:23,110 --> 00:17:24,650
and pulled something out of a bag...

280
00:17:25,180 --> 00:17:26,680
next to the bed.

281
00:17:26,820 --> 00:17:29,690
Something she had to keep track of
with alarms?

282
00:17:31,690 --> 00:17:33,590
She's drugging the chairman.

283
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:35,290
If we can find out what it is,

284
00:17:35,360 --> 00:17:36,990
we might be able to wake him up.

285
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:59,880
I've prepared
the necessary medical supplies.

286
00:18:00,050 --> 00:18:03,120
And the professional caregiver
for the chairman?

287
00:18:03,120 --> 00:18:04,250
Morning and evening.

288
00:18:04,760 --> 00:18:06,620
Have them come in twice a day
to look after him.

289
00:18:06,690 --> 00:18:08,360
Understood, ma'am.

290
00:18:08,630 --> 00:18:11,830
Where are the bodyguards?

291
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:14,200
We came back in such a hurry...

292
00:18:14,970 --> 00:18:16,230
I didn't have time to arrange it.

293
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:17,900
They'll be here tomorrow morning.

294
00:18:17,970 --> 00:18:20,640
Bodyguards are the priority,
not a caregiver.

295
00:18:20,640 --> 00:18:21,710
Yes, ma'am.

296
00:18:37,650 --> 00:18:39,520
Hey, what's going on
with Kim Myung Hui and Park Min Jun?

297
00:18:40,060 --> 00:18:43,090
Did he change his mind,
like she said?

298
00:18:43,090 --> 00:18:46,430
Yes. From what I overheard,
it seems that way.

299
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:51,000
Of course. If she says it's decided,
what can he do about it?

300
00:18:51,070 --> 00:18:52,170
I know, right?

301
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:57,110
If he hadn't given in,
you'd have tried to kill him again.

302
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:59,680
It's a relief we can just
split the company in half...

303
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:01,280
and be done with it.

304
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:02,750
"Done with it?" As if.

305
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:06,620
This isn't over until I kill
both Kim Myung Hui and Park Min Jun.

306
00:19:08,520 --> 00:19:09,520
Jung Ran!

307
00:19:09,590 --> 00:19:12,620
Since it's too risky to deal
with them both at the same time...

308
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:16,630
and Hyun Jun would flip out,
I'm holding back for now.

309
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:20,130
I have them reeled in
with the offer of half of Adele,

310
00:19:20,300 --> 00:19:22,270
but when I get a chance,
I'll finish them both off.

311
00:19:22,270 --> 00:19:23,270
Just you watch.

312
00:19:23,300 --> 00:19:24,470
Jung Ran, please.

313
00:19:25,870 --> 00:19:30,410
Get those terrible ideas
out of your head.

314
00:19:33,840 --> 00:19:34,850
Ms. Choi!

315
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:39,420
Who said you could come in?

316
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:43,050
I was just worried
about the chairman.

317
00:19:43,990 --> 00:19:44,990
But...

318
00:19:46,760 --> 00:19:48,530
Did he really collapse?

319
00:19:49,030 --> 00:19:51,600
Did you do this to him?
Will he never get up again?

320
00:19:51,660 --> 00:19:52,660
You...

321
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,870
How's that your business?

322
00:19:55,100 --> 00:19:57,130
Don't just stand there.
Get her out. Now.

323
00:19:57,130 --> 00:19:59,770
Right, of course. Come on, let's go.

324
00:19:59,900 --> 00:20:01,610
Come on, now.

325
00:20:17,420 --> 00:20:19,690
I get it, all right? Let go of me.

326
00:20:20,290 --> 00:20:23,430
I just want to see the chairman.
Why is everyone so on edge?

327
00:20:23,490 --> 00:20:26,160
You should just leave while you can.

328
00:20:26,700 --> 00:20:29,170
Nothing good will come
from you sticking around.

329
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:41,850
She really was drugging him?

330
00:20:42,650 --> 00:20:45,420
It was only for a second,
but I saw a syringe.

331
00:20:47,780 --> 00:20:51,090
I'm pretty sure
I came through for you this time.

332
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:53,590
Now it's your turn to help me out.

333
00:20:54,460 --> 00:20:57,060
If I get my job back,
I'll help you even more.

334
00:20:58,060 --> 00:21:02,900
Please, help me get my job back
so I can be with Min Jun.

335
00:21:04,300 --> 00:21:05,300
All right.

336
00:21:05,970 --> 00:21:07,440
I'll see you at the office tomorrow.

337
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:12,080
Yes, Mother. Thank you.

338
00:21:43,740 --> 00:21:45,610
So, what do you think,
now that you've seen them yourself?

339
00:21:47,840 --> 00:21:50,250
Everyone in the Adele family...

340
00:21:51,820 --> 00:21:53,580
They're all snobs...

341
00:21:56,190 --> 00:21:57,690
and monsters, aren't they?

342
00:22:07,460 --> 00:22:08,470
Then...

343
00:22:09,670 --> 00:22:11,300
we have to become just like them.

344
00:22:13,600 --> 00:22:16,970
I know it'll be hard,
but please work with your mother.

345
00:22:17,840 --> 00:22:20,510
You need to secure your place
as Adele's successor...

346
00:22:21,950 --> 00:22:23,410
for me to have a place there too.

347
00:22:26,450 --> 00:22:28,390
You may not see it this way,

348
00:22:28,720 --> 00:22:31,050
but this time while Chairman Park
is incapacitated...

349
00:22:32,090 --> 00:22:33,590
is an opportunity for me.

350
00:22:34,460 --> 00:22:38,660
I can finally do all the things
he stopped me from doing.

351
00:22:40,530 --> 00:22:41,670
Besides taking over the company,

352
00:22:42,430 --> 00:22:43,900
do you have another plan?

353
00:22:46,270 --> 00:22:47,470
My dad's car accident...

354
00:22:49,370 --> 00:22:50,640
from seven years ago.

355
00:22:51,610 --> 00:22:53,640
I'm going to get the case reopened.

356
00:22:55,410 --> 00:22:58,920
Just because Chairman Park collapsed
doesn't mean his crimes disappear.

357
00:22:59,820 --> 00:23:03,590
I'll expose his crimes to the world
and get the case reopened.

358
00:23:12,500 --> 00:23:13,500
Hyun Jun.

359
00:23:16,470 --> 00:23:17,530
I...

360
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:21,570
I want to use this opportunity
for everything it's worth.

361
00:23:22,570 --> 00:23:25,040
Taking over Adele just got easier,

362
00:23:25,540 --> 00:23:27,140
and with him gone,

363
00:23:27,140 --> 00:23:29,810
I can finally expose
what really happened in the past.

364
00:23:36,090 --> 00:23:39,490
I know this is hard for you
to come to terms with.

365
00:23:42,030 --> 00:23:43,590
If this is what you want,

366
00:23:46,630 --> 00:23:48,130
what choice do I have?

367
00:23:51,540 --> 00:23:52,940
I'll just have to grit my teeth...

368
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:56,970
and bear it.

369
00:24:09,020 --> 00:24:10,020
I'm sorry.

370
00:24:22,830 --> 00:24:25,070
You. Sit right here.

371
00:24:26,140 --> 00:24:30,010
The bodyguards arrive tomorrow,
so I need you on guard tonight.

372
00:24:31,110 --> 00:24:32,180
Stand guard?

373
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:35,380
It'd be weird to sleep beside him,
wouldn't it?

374
00:24:35,450 --> 00:24:37,480
I'm going to the annex
to get some rest,

375
00:24:37,650 --> 00:24:39,350
so watch him carefully
until morning.

376
00:24:42,520 --> 00:24:45,620
Once the bodyguards get here,
no one can see the chairman.

377
00:24:45,820 --> 00:24:47,960
Make sure no one gets in to see him.

378
00:25:06,610 --> 00:25:09,810
Are these about my dad's accident?

379
00:25:09,810 --> 00:25:10,850
That's right.

380
00:25:11,210 --> 00:25:14,050
It's information
on Dr. Baek and Temi Bio.

381
00:25:14,720 --> 00:25:16,720
I've compiled everything,
from Choi Sam Sik's transfer...

382
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:17,920
of Temi Bio to Adele...

383
00:25:18,120 --> 00:25:19,620
to suspicions...

384
00:25:19,620 --> 00:25:22,160
that Dr. Baek's suicide
may have been staged.

385
00:25:22,490 --> 00:25:24,790
I was putting it together
to request a new investigation,

386
00:25:25,060 --> 00:25:26,900
but I still don't have
any hard evidence,

387
00:25:27,200 --> 00:25:28,600
so I've just been sitting on it.

388
00:25:29,400 --> 00:25:33,600
So, why the sudden interest?
What are you planning to do with it?

389
00:25:34,240 --> 00:25:36,740
It may not be enough
to reopen the case,

390
00:25:37,040 --> 00:25:41,010
but I think it's enough
to stir up public interest.

391
00:25:41,410 --> 00:25:43,480
You're trying to sway
public opinion?

392
00:25:44,080 --> 00:25:46,250
Aside from taking over Adele,

393
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:49,820
I'm going to expose the truth
about the accident from seven years ago.

394
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:53,220
While Chairman Park can't interfere,

395
00:25:53,960 --> 00:25:55,660
we have to make our move.

396
00:25:56,360 --> 00:25:57,960
So that he can't avoid...

397
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,960
a reinvestigation
even after he wakes up,

398
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:04,330
I'm going to make
some serious noise.

399
00:26:34,800 --> 00:26:35,870
Taking a quick rest...

400
00:26:37,300 --> 00:26:39,140
won't hurt anyone.

401
00:26:39,770 --> 00:26:40,840
Oh, man...

402
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:38,360
Both Butler Ok...

403
00:27:39,100 --> 00:27:41,660
and Ms. Choi said
they definitely saw it.

404
00:28:20,500 --> 00:28:23,410
It's such a pain having to drug him
on a schedule.

405
00:28:30,950 --> 00:28:33,050
Figures. I knew this would happen.

406
00:28:33,780 --> 00:28:35,790
You're not just dozing off,
you're fully asleep?

407
00:28:56,370 --> 00:28:57,370
Kim Myung Hui, you.

408
00:28:59,110 --> 00:29:00,310
What do you think
you're doing in here?

409
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:05,950
Answer me!
I asked what you were doing in here.

410
00:29:07,580 --> 00:29:09,350
You call this taking care of him?

411
00:29:09,690 --> 00:29:10,690
What?

412
00:29:10,690 --> 00:29:12,660
I heard a weird noise and came in.

413
00:29:12,920 --> 00:29:14,160
He was having trouble breathing.

414
00:29:14,320 --> 00:29:16,530
He would've been in real danger
if I hadn't stepped in.

415
00:29:17,690 --> 00:29:20,900
Showing off your old nursing skills,
are you?

416
00:29:21,760 --> 00:29:23,500
Stop your grandstanding
and get out. Now.

417
00:29:23,830 --> 00:29:25,340
Don't you ever set foot
in here again.

418
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:29,510
Then do your job right,

419
00:29:30,070 --> 00:29:31,070
so I don't have to.

420
00:29:33,510 --> 00:29:35,680
Why that...

421
00:29:36,250 --> 00:29:37,710
The nerve of her.

422
00:30:07,380 --> 00:30:10,980
So instead of finding the drug,
you drew the chairman's blood?

423
00:30:11,410 --> 00:30:14,150
To analyze it
and see what drug was used?

424
00:30:14,350 --> 00:30:16,520
Jung Ran didn't leave
the drugs behind,

425
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:17,950
so I had to find another way.

426
00:30:18,490 --> 00:30:21,620
Take this
to Mrs. Han at Ihwachae right now.

427
00:30:22,230 --> 00:30:24,030
Once we know what drug she used,

428
00:30:24,390 --> 00:30:26,900
we should be able to find a way
to wake up the chairman.

429
00:30:27,360 --> 00:30:29,000
Yes, understood.

430
00:30:31,300 --> 00:30:32,400
Can I go with her?

431
00:30:32,670 --> 00:30:34,840
I want to do anything I can
for Father.

432
00:30:36,140 --> 00:30:37,970
Okay, but be careful.

433
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:40,710
I won't let anything happen to him.

434
00:30:42,510 --> 00:30:45,950
Once the chairman wakes up,
Manager Kang will change his mind.

435
00:30:46,420 --> 00:30:48,520
The power of attorney
and medical records...

436
00:30:48,520 --> 00:30:50,690
she had him draw up under duress
will all be invalidated,

437
00:30:51,420 --> 00:30:54,190
and we can turn this around
in an instant.

438
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:57,960
Got it. Secretary Jung and I will
deliver the blood sample safely.

439
00:31:13,340 --> 00:31:14,880
Stay alert at all times.

440
00:31:15,450 --> 00:31:18,880
No one, and I mean no one,
is allowed to visit the chairman.

441
00:31:27,660 --> 00:31:29,190
Hello, this is Kim Myung Hui.

442
00:31:30,230 --> 00:31:33,400
We've identified the drug.

443
00:31:34,360 --> 00:31:35,370
There's a chance...

444
00:31:35,830 --> 00:31:39,040
we may be able to bring
Chairman Park around.

445
00:32:24,210 --> 00:32:27,180
(Pearl in Red)

446
00:32:27,350 --> 00:32:29,220
Promise me that Father
will be the last one.

447
00:32:29,520 --> 00:32:31,690
Hurting people
while claiming it's for my sake?

448
00:32:32,020 --> 00:32:33,090
That has to stop now.

449
00:32:33,360 --> 00:32:37,060
Promise me that, and I'll be
the greedy snob who wants Adele.

450
00:32:37,530 --> 00:32:39,000
I can't predict
how Min Jun really feels.

451
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:42,830
One moment he's sweet to me,
and the next, he's distant.

452
00:32:42,830 --> 00:32:46,140
I'm afraid he'll change
when his memory comes back.

453
00:32:46,140 --> 00:32:49,010
What's going on?
Nothing happened, did it?

454
00:32:49,910 --> 00:32:54,540
Oh Jung Ran, how dare you...

455
00:32:56,080 --> 00:32:58,080
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
